          saving_account_title_: 'Saving Account',
          saving_account_description_: 'With our savings account services you can keep deposits on your saving bank account and earn the smallest amount of profit as an interest with many more facilities & services provided by the Bank. Also you can withdraw money anytime. We offer you a saving account with a host of products like SMS Banking allow you to update your account information as per your need like account balance enquiry, last 3 transactions, cheque status, etc. All the services are offered to you with very simple terms and conditions and minimal charges.',
